val parquetFileOffers = sqlContext.read.parquet("/home/ama/sidana/calypso_kk_june_data/offerView/it/2016/*/*/*.parquet")
val uniqueUsersOffers = parquetFileOffers.select("userId").distinct
val uniqueOfferViewsOffers = parquetFileOffers.select("offerViewId").distinct
val uniqueOfferCategoriesOffers = parquetFileOffers.select("category").distinct
val offerIdOffers = parquetFileOffers.select(substring_index(parquetFileOffers("offerViewId"),"-",1))
val uniqueOfferIdOffers = offerIdOffers.select("substring_index(offerViewId,-,1)").distinct
val uniqueUserOfferPairs = parquetFileOffers.select("userId","offerViewId").distinct

parquetFileOffers.count //counting number of offer views
uniqueUsersOffers.count //counting number of unique users in impressions
uniqueOfferViewsOffers.count //counting number of unique offerViews in impressions
uniqueOfferCategoriesOffers.count //counting number of categories in impressions
uniqueOfferIdOffers.count // counting number of offer in impressions
uniqueUserOfferPairs.count // counting number of unique user-offer  pairs in impressions
